headline: Evergy Announces Third Quarter 2024 Results, Increases Quarterly Dividend, Reaffirms 2024 Guidance, Establishes 2025 Guidance
summary: KANSAS CITY, Mo., November 07, 2024--Evergy, Inc. (NASDAQ: EVRG) today announced third quarter 2024 GAAP earnings of $465.6 million, or $2.02 per share, compared to GAAP earnings of $351.6 million, or $1.53 per share, for the third quarter 2023.
